lead_paragraph: Democratic U.S. presidential candidate Hillary Clinton announced a new plan to give businesses two-year tax credits for sharing profits with workers at a New Hampshire campaign stop Thursday.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Proposes Tax Cuts for Profit-Sharing Firms
